node.text:
@nasa and @spacex are targeting April 15, 2022 for the launch of the Crew-4 mission:
. 
Crew-4 will carry @nasa astronauts @astro_kjell and @astro_farmerbob , @europeanspaceagency astronaut Samantha Cristoforetti , and a fourth crew member yet to be named!
.
SpaceX & NASA crew rotation schedule:
. 
Crew-3 launch – Oct 31
Crew-2 return – Nov 15 to Nov 30
Crew-4 launch – April 15
Crew-3 return – April 22 to April 30
.
.
.
.
.
.
.
